default&#xa0;
default              
defaultQ82default 
defaultMike defaultCrockartdefault:default I realise that this is asking how long is a piece of string, but if we have figured out when the likely start of the consultation is, do we have a time scale for when it would finish and any results might be available?
default              
defaultChris Chew:default The usual procedure is to consult for between six to 12 weeks, so we would need to consider what the appropriate period was. For a very specialist subject such as this, which affects quite a narrow group of people, a shorter consultation period might be more appropriate, but we are open to suggestions and comments.
