defaultQ98default 
defaultChair:default Secretary of State, I want to turn now to the very important issue of the export approvals by this Government and the previous Government of dual-use chemicals to 
defaultSyria
default, in particular, sodium fluoride and potassium fluoride. They are dual-use because, in addition to their civil uses, they are precursor chemicals in the manufacture of 
defaultsarin
